04T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"個 Agenda 錯哂<br />\n<br />\n前線革命緊，後面既五大訴求卻係妄想政權會進行改革<br />\n一個推翻政府，一個希望政府聆聽<br />\n結果 ，義士變烈士，次次送頭<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可 (對現任政府有幻想)<br />\n光復香港，時代革命 (希望重組政府)<br />\n<br />\n依兩句放埋一齊會有邏輯問題<br />\n<br />\n所謂兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪應該爬同一座山呀<br />\n<br />\n如果林鄭聽日下台，你地有咩準備呀？<br />\n<br />\n快啲諗呀，殺到尼喇</span></span>"},{"pid":"daa6d9b982bf7202af45bdf6099093aba7861deb","tid":1539092,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"呢<br />\n<br />\n尼你老母"},{"pid":"ac2f07c58737ac424a0a7b012dfafc472bf07b80","tid":1539092,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nM39Tkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnM39Tkd.jpg&h=e2a199c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太子仲有幾個生死未卜<br />\n又贏？贏喺邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0d5fdbf0dad114c49be6fc9803069b6ae68c9a","tid":1539092,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c54d39533df39e338d3b2b9e3d8e1fedb350b6e","tid":1539092,"uid":258159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尼件事並不尋常<br />\n唔可以掉以輕心<br />\n政府分明係想瓦解運動<br />\n分化手足<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n撤回~是分化勇武、和理非的手段<br />\n<br />\n反送中 不只這條例 還有施政行為:<br />\n警濫權 用致命手法每棍打頭<br />\n企業白色恐怖<br />\n以言入罪<br />\n文革潮<br />\n教育界實施評分制<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n分別在於用手足的血換取:<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n義士因布袋受傷<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲 (元朗、太子)<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n失去9位生命<br />\n被性逼害女手足<br />\n市民食催淚彈<br />\n港鐵亂放催淚彈<br />\n被捕 1200個